WEBVTT

00:00:07.440 --> 00:00:08.239
Where did the photo come from?

00:00:09.960 --> 00:00:11.319
I was about to ask you that.

00:00:11.319 --> 00:00:12.479
Who is the person in this photo?

00:00:12.479 --> 00:00:13.399
What's your relationship to him?

00:00:13.399 --> 00:00:14.279
Who is he?

00:01:19.760 --> 00:01:20.919
That really did the trick.

00:01:21.400 --> 00:01:22.559
The sound of her grinding teeth

00:01:22.839 --> 00:01:24.279
actually cured my nightmares.

00:01:31.599 --> 00:01:32.519
You're back.

00:01:32.559 --> 00:01:33.800
Where did you go so early?

00:01:33.959 --> 00:01:34.720
Morning run?

00:01:35.440 --> 00:01:35.959
Yeah.

00:01:37.639 --> 00:01:38.519
I just made breakfast.

00:01:38.519 --> 00:01:39.519
Come have a bite.

00:01:46.239 --> 00:01:47.279
What happened to your hand?

00:01:48.599 --> 00:01:49.239
My hand?

00:01:49.239 --> 00:01:49.959
Well...

00:01:50.120 --> 00:01:52.120
I don't exactly sleep still.

00:01:52.720 --> 00:01:55.160
Last night I dreamed I was beating you up,

00:01:55.199 --> 00:01:56.559
and I accidentally banged it.

00:02:00.279 --> 00:02:01.000
I made breakfast.

00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:01.800
Come have a bite.

00:02:01.800 --> 00:02:02.720
It's nice and hot.

00:02:03.559 --> 00:02:04.879
I don't have a breakfast habit.

00:02:05.760 --> 00:02:06.959
Now that you've got me,

00:02:07.120 --> 00:02:08.440
you'll have that habit too.

00:02:09.039 --> 00:02:10.119
My habit is

00:02:10.679 --> 00:02:11.399
not having you.

00:02:25.440 --> 00:02:26.160
Lu Yi.

00:02:26.199 --> 00:02:26.880
Don't rush.

00:02:26.919 --> 00:02:27.679
Steady your breathing.

00:02:27.800 --> 00:02:28.440
Three points in a line.

00:02:29.639 --> 00:02:30.520
Tripitaka.

00:02:30.520 --> 00:02:31.759
My ears are growing calluses.

00:02:31.759 --> 00:02:32.880
Can you stop talking?

00:02:32.880 --> 00:02:34.639
I'm just off today.

00:02:36.320 --> 00:02:37.119
I'm done playing.

00:02:37.880 --> 00:02:38.639
If your mind isn't calm,

00:02:38.919 --> 00:02:39.960
of course you won't hit it right.

00:02:41.080 --> 00:02:42.399
I don't need you to tell me.

00:02:42.839 --> 00:02:44.600
You talk like you're so good.

00:02:46.639 --> 00:02:47.960
I'm better than you, anyway.

00:02:50.759 --> 00:02:51.240
Fine.

00:02:51.360 --> 00:02:52.440
Then dare to compete with me?

00:02:52.839 --> 00:02:54.800
Whoever loses has to

00:02:55.639 --> 00:02:56.919
do the dishes for one week.

00:02:59.559 --> 00:03:00.240
Okay.

00:03:01.919 --> 00:03:02.639
But

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:03.880
if I win,

00:03:04.360 --> 00:03:05.559
besides doing the dishes,

00:03:05.720 --> 00:03:07.080
that lousy sofa bed of yours

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:08.960
moves back another ten centimeters.

00:03:11.199 --> 00:03:12.000
Bring it on.

00:03:22.600 --> 00:03:23.600
Three points.

00:03:25.440 --> 00:03:26.240
Move aside.

00:03:32.880 --> 00:03:34.360
Bull's-eye.

00:03:36.360 --> 00:03:37.160
Remember to do the dishes.

00:03:43.000 --> 00:03:44.520
Starting today,

00:03:45.440 --> 00:03:46.679
I'm not eating dinner.

00:03:47.440 --> 00:03:48.360
That's one less bowl to wash.

00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:24.640
You're very obedient.

00:04:25.480 --> 00:04:27.000
This is your reward.

00:04:33.880 --> 00:04:34.760
What bit me here?

00:04:36.040 --> 00:04:37.119
Why are there mosquitoes?

00:04:40.359 --> 00:04:41.679
There seems to be a bad smell.

00:04:41.839 --> 00:04:42.640
A bad smell?

00:04:56.839 --> 00:04:57.480
Come on, hurry.

00:05:13.679 --> 00:05:14.480
What's going on?

00:05:17.359 --> 00:05:18.480
The deceased is female.

00:05:19.320 --> 00:05:21.119
Preliminarily, the time of death

00:05:21.799 --> 00:05:23.239
was at least over a week ago.

00:05:24.239 --> 00:05:26.239
She was curled up in a fetal position,

00:05:26.559 --> 00:05:28.279
stuffed headfirst into a tree hollow.

00:05:28.760 --> 00:05:30.040
The body is decomposed and bloated.

00:05:30.760 --> 00:05:32.720
Identifying her will be difficult.

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:34.679
As for other specifics,

00:05:34.679 --> 00:05:35.839
we need to wait for the autopsy report.

00:05:37.480 --> 00:05:38.079
Come on.

00:05:38.559 --> 00:05:39.440
Carry her out.

00:05:46.559 --> 00:05:47.440
If you need to vomit, do it.

00:05:48.839 --> 00:05:49.640
I don't need to.

00:05:53.519 --> 00:05:54.720
What were you doing last night?

00:05:54.880 --> 00:05:56.480
At the time, we were

00:05:57.279 --> 00:05:58.519
watching the stars.

00:05:59.320 --> 00:06:01.119
Then we suddenly smelled something foul,

00:06:01.119 --> 00:06:03.000
and then we found this.

00:06:03.000 --> 00:06:03.679
Right, right, right.

00:06:04.079 --> 00:06:05.600
I was scared to death.

00:06:08.720 --> 00:06:10.239
Take them down to rest first.

00:06:19.040 --> 00:06:19.640
Captain.

00:06:21.160 --> 00:06:22.799
There are basically no signs of a struggle.

00:06:23.440 --> 00:06:24.320
But the fallen leaves are thick,

00:06:24.320 --> 00:06:25.920
so lifting footprints will be difficult.

00:06:27.239 --> 00:06:28.720
This doesn't look like the primary scene.

00:06:29.040 --> 00:06:30.359
It's more like a dump site.

00:06:42.200 --> 00:06:42.959
Then let's do this.

00:06:43.079 --> 00:06:45.000
Check recent missing persons reports.

00:06:45.440 --> 00:06:47.440
Focus on female cases.

00:06:48.160 --> 00:06:48.920
Lin Shen, Lu Yi.

00:06:49.640 --> 00:06:51.640
You two come with me to the morgue.

00:06:52.799 --> 00:06:54.279
Shi Lei, stay here and watch things.

00:06:56.839 --> 00:06:57.600
I'm going too.

00:06:57.600 --> 00:06:58.320
What are you going for?

00:06:58.320 --> 00:06:59.200
Stay here and watch.

00:07:12.679 --> 00:07:13.399
Zhou Shuyu.

00:07:13.880 --> 00:07:14.480
Female.

00:07:14.480 --> 00:07:15.279
Twenty-eight years old.

00:07:15.519 --> 00:07:17.200
Teacher at Huacheng Art College.

00:07:20.359 --> 00:07:22.119
Cause of death was a skull fracture,

00:07:22.279 --> 00:07:23.399
caused by blunt force trauma.

00:07:28.839 --> 00:07:30.079
There is a knife wound on her left wrist,

00:07:30.480 --> 00:07:31.359
but the cut is shallow.

00:07:31.519 --> 00:07:32.079
It wasn't fatal.

00:07:32.279 --> 00:07:33.320
Is there any possi-

00:07:53.160 --> 00:07:53.880
Rookie.

00:07:57.119 --> 00:07:57.839
One week ago,

00:07:58.320 --> 00:07:59.119
the police station received

00:07:59.119 --> 00:08:01.320
a report that Zhou Shuyu was missing.

00:08:01.320 --> 00:08:03.920
The caller was her fiance, Zhang Chongyang.

00:08:03.959 --> 00:08:04.480
The two of them

00:08:04.480 --> 00:08:06.480
are both teachers at Huacheng Art College.

00:08:12.399 --> 00:08:14.000
Zhou Shuyu's clothes and jewelry

00:08:14.200 --> 00:08:15.600
cost more than my yearly salary.

00:08:16.480 --> 00:08:17.480
They're all big brands.

00:08:18.440 --> 00:08:19.600
Even Haozi knows this stuff?

00:08:22.279 --> 00:08:24.440
Zhou Shuyu's style of dress

00:08:24.440 --> 00:08:25.760
is pretty elegant and poised.

00:08:26.480 --> 00:08:28.399
She doesn't seem like the type for bright red nails.

00:08:29.200 --> 00:08:30.200
Not necessarily.

00:08:30.760 --> 00:08:32.000
Everyone has two sides.

00:08:33.799 --> 00:08:35.840
But taking such a beautiful woman

00:08:35.840 --> 00:08:37.359
and dumping her in a tree hollow like that...

00:08:37.359 --> 00:08:38.440
Look at her body.

00:08:38.919 --> 00:08:40.359
It's swollen up like a balloon.

00:08:40.679 --> 00:08:42.200
Her eyeballs and tongue are bulging out.

00:08:42.960 --> 00:08:44.559
That's a psycho opening the door for a psycho.

00:08:44.559 --> 00:08:44.919
All right.

00:08:44.919 --> 00:08:45.799
Psycho to the core.

00:08:47.239 --> 00:08:48.479
Let's quickly divide the tasks.

00:08:50.679 --> 00:08:51.599
Lin Shen, Lu Yi.

00:08:51.599 --> 00:08:53.400
You two go talk to Zhang Chongyang.

00:08:53.679 --> 00:08:54.400
Shitou.

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:55.880
Haozi.

00:08:56.159 --> 00:08:58.400
Go check Zhou Shuyu's social connections

00:08:58.400 --> 00:09:00.280
and her recent movements.

00:09:00.919 --> 00:09:01.359
Guozi and I'll support you.

00:09:01.359 --> 00:09:02.840
Guozi and I'll support you.

00:09:02.880 --> 00:09:03.320
All right.

00:09:03.640 --> 00:09:03.960
Okay.

00:09:03.960 --> 00:09:04.919
Yes, sir.

00:09:30.200 --> 00:09:30.840
Hello

00:09:31.200 --> 00:09:31.679
And you two are?

00:09:31.679 --> 00:09:33.320
We're from the Criminal Investigation Brigade.

00:09:34.080 --> 00:09:35.080
There are some things about Zhou Shuyu

00:09:35.080 --> 00:09:36.039
we need to ask you about.

00:09:37.960 --> 00:09:38.960
Has Xiao Yu been found?

00:09:38.960 --> 00:09:39.719
Where is she?

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:43.559
First, tell us

00:09:43.559 --> 00:09:45.159
what happened the day she disappeared.

00:09:45.440 --> 00:09:46.440
Where were you that day?

00:09:49.400 --> 00:09:50.479
When I left that day,

00:09:50.479 --> 00:09:51.359
she was perfectly fine.

00:09:51.760 --> 00:09:54.479
She even said she'd fix her wedding dress.

00:09:54.840 --> 00:09:56.919
But when I got back, she was gone.

00:09:57.400 --> 00:09:59.239
I thought she'd gone shopping with friends.

00:10:00.039 --> 00:10:01.960
But she never came back, no matter how long I waited.

00:10:03.520 --> 00:10:05.760
Was there anything unusual before she vanished?

00:10:06.359 --> 00:10:07.200
Did you two argue,

00:10:07.320 --> 00:10:08.640
or have any physical conflict?

00:10:08.960 --> 00:10:10.159
How could that be?

00:10:10.559 --> 00:10:11.719
Our relationship was great.

00:10:11.719 --> 00:10:12.599
How could I possibly dare

00:10:13.440 --> 00:10:14.840
to ever hit her?

00:10:18.599 --> 00:10:19.200
Wait, that isn't right.

00:10:19.919 --> 00:10:20.640
Hold on.

00:10:21.919 --> 00:10:22.919
You're homicide detectives.

00:10:23.159 --> 00:10:25.239
What does a disappearance have to do with you?

00:10:25.719 --> 00:10:27.119
Zhou Shuyu has already been killed.

00:10:27.359 --> 00:10:28.159
What?

00:10:28.799 --> 00:10:30.559
In the woods outside the city,

00:10:30.559 --> 00:10:31.840
we found her body.

00:10:36.200 --> 00:10:36.880
No way.

00:10:37.159 --> 00:10:37.960
How is that possible?

00:10:40.440 --> 00:10:41.239
Xiao Yu...

00:10:41.840 --> 00:10:42.640
Impossible.

00:10:46.080 --> 00:10:47.479
Xiao Yu can't be dead.

00:10:51.479 --> 00:10:52.280
Xiao Yu...

00:10:53.880 --> 00:10:54.679
Mr. Zhang.

00:10:55.840 --> 00:10:56.640
Mr. Zhang.

00:10:58.200 --> 00:10:58.919
Sorry.

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:00.440
We urgently need to go to

00:11:00.440 --> 00:11:02.520
the home you shared with Zhou Shuyu

00:11:02.520 --> 00:11:03.559
and conduct an investigation.

00:11:03.559 --> 00:11:04.599
Please cooperate with us.

00:11:11.679 --> 00:11:12.239
Okay.

00:11:12.719 --> 00:11:13.719
I'll fully cooperate.

00:11:14.880 --> 00:11:15.479
Please,

00:11:15.479 --> 00:11:16.679
catch the killer as soon as possible

00:11:16.960 --> 00:11:18.440
and get justice for Xiao Yu.

00:11:21.919 --> 00:11:22.919
Please, follow me.

00:11:38.080 --> 00:11:40.320
Did you smell blood just now?

00:11:47.679 --> 00:11:48.239
Come in.

00:11:48.359 --> 00:11:49.520
Officers, please come in.

00:11:49.760 --> 00:11:50.640
The place is a bit messy.

00:11:50.640 --> 00:11:51.440
With Xiao Yu not home,

00:11:51.440 --> 00:11:52.440
I couldn't be bothered to tidy up.

00:11:52.440 --> 00:11:53.320
Do you need to change shoes?

00:11:53.640 --> 00:11:54.159
No need.

00:11:54.239 --> 00:11:54.719
Let's go.

00:11:54.719 --> 00:11:55.960
These shoes are hard to take off anyway.

00:11:59.719 --> 00:12:00.440
Please, this way.

00:12:02.080 --> 00:12:02.960
Mr. Zhang,

00:12:03.719 --> 00:12:06.359
your home is exquisitely decorated.

00:12:08.440 --> 00:12:09.440
This sofa,

00:12:10.239 --> 00:12:11.479
imported Italian leather.

00:12:12.679 --> 00:12:14.359
These are all things Xiao Yu liked.

00:12:14.479 --> 00:12:16.039
She had high standards for quality of life.

00:12:16.320 --> 00:12:18.960
She even designed her own dresses herself.

00:12:19.960 --> 00:12:20.599
Further inside.

00:12:32.320 --> 00:12:34.000
This was my birthday gift to Xiao Yu.

00:12:34.400 --> 00:12:36.119
It's the piece I'm most proud of.

00:12:36.880 --> 00:12:37.719
At the same time,

00:12:38.640 --> 00:12:40.280
it also earned me a special reward from her.

00:12:44.760 --> 00:12:45.440
Please wait a moment.

00:12:45.960 --> 00:12:47.119
I'll pour you both a cup of coffee.

00:12:47.719 --> 00:12:48.039
Thanks.

00:12:48.039 --> 00:12:48.520
Thank you.

00:12:52.840 --> 00:12:54.239
Artists really are different.

00:12:55.559 --> 00:12:56.840
Have you ever gotten some kind of

00:12:56.840 --> 00:12:58.159
special gift from someone?

00:13:04.000 --> 00:13:04.679
That's strange.

00:13:04.840 --> 00:13:06.559
Why do I keep smelling this faint

00:13:06.799 --> 00:13:08.239
trace of blood?